flowchart TD
    Start([School Admin Login]) --> Dashboard[View Dashboard<br/>Stats & Alerts]
    Dashboard --> Choice{What to do?}

    Choice -->|Manage| Teachers[Invite Teachers<br/>Assign Classes]
    Choice -->|Manage| Students[Invite Students<br/>Enroll in Classes]
    Choice -->|Setup| Curriculum[Upload Documents<br/>Define Subjects]
    Choice -->|Monitor| Analytics[View Analytics<br/>Performance Metrics]

    Teachers --> Assign[Assign to Classes<br/>Set Permissions]
    Students --> Enroll[Bulk Enrollment<br/>Class Assignment]
    Curriculum --> Process[Auto-Process<br/>Chunk & Embed]
    Analytics --> Insights[Teacher Utilization<br/>Class Performance<br/>Subject Distribution]

    Assign --> Review[Review Dashboard<br/>Check Alerts]
    Enroll --> Review
    Process --> Review
    Insights --> Review

    Review --> End([Logout])

    style Start fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#10b981,color:#fff
    style Analytics fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style End fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
